Analyze Your Data
Salesforce Analytics Tools
Reports and Dashboards
Manage Your Reports and Dashboards on Analytics Home
Subscribe to or Schedule Dashboards
Set up automatic dashboard refreshes and receive refreshed dashboard results by email on a schedule that you set.
Required Editions: Essentials, Group, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, Developer Editions
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience

Subscribe to Dashboards in Lightning Experience
Rather than manually refreshing a dashboard, subscribe yourself or others to receive refreshed dashboard results by email on a schedule.

Schedule a Dashboard Refresh in Salesforce Classic
Schedule dashboards to refresh them daily, weekly, or monthly, and receive refreshed dashboard results by email.
Control Dashboard Data Visibility
title: Automatically Refreshing Salesforce Dashboards
